cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.MM 

The paper is about pedestrian detection using deep learning approaches, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves high-level semantic feature detection, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The method also involves scale prediction, which is related to robotics (cs.RO) and multimedia (cs.MM).
